[
    {
        "text": "ï»¿Sometimes our mind wanders.",
        "startTime": 7283,
        "endTime": 9532,
        "slowStartTime": 11074,
        "slowEndTime": 14523
    },
    {
        "text": "And when we snap back to reality,...",
        "startTime": 10089,
        "endTime": 11962,
        "slowStartTime": 15284,
        "slowEndTime": 18168
    },
    {
        "text": "...we have no idea what we missed or how long we were gone.",
        "startTime": 12434,
        "endTime": 15315,
        "slowStartTime": 18801,
        "slowEndTime": 23197
    },
    {
        "text": "Daydreaming isn't the only thing that causes this inattention blindness.",
        "startTime": 16376,
        "endTime": 20104,
        "slowStartTime": 24714,
        "slowEndTime": 30381
    },
    {
        "text": "When we talk on the phone while driving,...",
        "startTime": 20480,
        "endTime": 22202,
        "slowStartTime": 30870,
        "slowEndTime": 33528
    },
    {
        "text": "...there are periods when we go blind to our environment without realizing them.",
        "startTime": 22731,
        "endTime": 26731,
        "slowStartTime": 34246,
        "slowEndTime": 40321
    },
    {
        "text": "So billboards, cars, kids playing, even stop signs and red lights can pass us by unnoticed.",
        "startTime": 27334,
        "endTime": 33844,
        "slowStartTime": 41151,
        "slowEndTime": 50991
    },
    {
        "text": "Certain things may seem harmless.",
        "startTime": 35016,
        "endTime": 37062,
        "slowStartTime": 52674,
        "slowEndTime": 55818
    },
    {
        "text": "But some activities just aren't safe to combine.",
        "startTime": 37753,
        "endTime": 43743,
        "slowStartTime": 56779,
        "slowEndTime": 65840
    },
    {
        "text": "Our brain is not wired to pay attention to more than one complex task at a time.",
        "startTime": 44831,
        "endTime": 49459,
        "slowStartTime": 67396,
        "slowEndTime": 74413
    },
    {
        "text": "What we're actually doing when we think we're multitasking...",
        "startTime": 49846,
        "endTime": 52722,
        "slowStartTime": 74919,
        "slowEndTime": 79308
    },
    {
        "text": "...is quickly shifting our focus from one activity to another.",
        "startTime": 52997,
        "endTime": 56342,
        "slowStartTime": 79646,
        "slowEndTime": 84738
    },
    {
        "text": "So while our mind is engaged in applying makeup, arguing with a backseat driver,...",
        "startTime": 56742,
        "endTime": 61163,
        "slowStartTime": 85263,
        "slowEndTime": 91970
    },
    {
        "text": "...fumbling for a water bottle, or a conversation, it's blind to the road.",
        "startTime": 61529,
        "endTime": 65763,
        "slowStartTime": 92443,
        "slowEndTime": 98869
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, drivers are four times more likely to crash while talking on the phone...",
        "startTime": 66300,
        "endTime": 70512,
        "slowStartTime": 99600,
        "slowEndTime": 105993
    },
    {
        "text": "...and 23 times more likely while texting.",
        "startTime": 71187,
        "endTime": 73718,
        "slowStartTime": 106930,
        "slowEndTime": 110802
    },
    {
        "text": "Driving can feel uneventful,...",
        "startTime": 74769,
        "endTime": 77144,
        "slowStartTime": 112304,
        "slowEndTime": 115941
    },
    {
        "text": "...but it really takes our full attention to keep the car on the road.",
        "startTime": 77419,
        "endTime": 80723,
        "slowStartTime": 116278,
        "slowEndTime": 121309
    },
    {
        "text": "We're surrounded by distractions that can hijack our focus.",
        "startTime": 81126,
        "endTime": 84388,
        "slowStartTime": 121839,
        "slowEndTime": 126807
    },
    {
        "text": "Whether we let them is up to us.",
        "startTime": 85197,
        "endTime": 88561,
        "slowStartTime": 127945,
        "slowEndTime": 133067
    }
]